{
  "texts": [
    "Addressing this issue requires a comprehensive and nuanced approach.",
    "Foremost, it is necessary to introduce an understanding of the importance of academic honesty and the negative implications of plagiarism on students' moral development and the integrity of their learning experience.",
    "This involves having clear policies and consequences surrounding academic dishonesty.",
    "The author has experience working with students unaware of what is and is not academic misconduct.",
    "This is particularly pronounced with international students who may be more familiar with academic best practices and ethical codes of conduct from their home country."
  ]
}